Please check the mobile phone network status first, open the network;
If it still cannot be solved, please try to open the application details in the system Settings and check whether the app permission allows the network (note whether the release is only traffic or traffic or wifi);
Still not solved, please try to open the app and tap 'Me' in the main screen. 'Support '&gt; 'Initial boot', release all permissions in permissions, and then go to 'I '&gt; 'Clean Up' deletes all persistent contents and restarts the application.
